{
 "name": "RPlog_Party_Planning_and_Other_Pursuits",
 "title": "Party Planning and Other Pursuits",
 "summary": "At his island keep on Yaeguero Isle off Caspar, the scientist Basca Starker hosts the Jedi Jessalyn Valios and the Kubaz fashion designer Zubindi to plan a formal gala. Over chilled fruit drinks beneath a canopy, Basca -- a veteran of the Sariphage plague whose estate was a gift from a grateful Caspar -- reveals his plans for the celebration while the artist Zubindi muses over designs and Jessalyn, distracted by her own emotional turmoil, looks on. As the day unfolds, the conversation drifts from party logistics to a budding, flirtatious alliance between Basca and Jessalyn, culminating in an intimate understanding between the two.",
